{"tid":2398303,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"沈祖堯：若社會不能一朝一夕改變，青年人應該望遠啲望闊啲！","createTime":"2021-02-07T07:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T07:45:40.000Z","uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"574e7a17ab4c289876d6082237f4c09a2d02d084","tid":2398303,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】沈祖堯醫生，2003年SARS時獲《時代》雜誌評為「亞洲英雄」，也曾是香港中文大學校長，深受學生愛戴。前年反修例運動已不是校長，為了中大衝突，他由沙田醫院跑回校園，全身濕透只為救助傷者。他本月將離開工作了30多年的威爾斯親王醫院，準備到新加坡工作，臨別向年輕人寄語，「看長遠一點和看闊一點，社會不是一朝一夕能改變的話，還有很多日子去努力、去做好自己」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20210207/s00002/1612636927791/【周日人物】反修例衝突-跑回中大為救傷者-沈祖堯寄語年輕人看遠一點\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210207%2Fs00002%2F1612636927791%2F%E3%80%90%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E3%80%91%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%B7%91%E5%9B%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%82%BA%E6%95%91%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85-%E6%B2%88%E7%A5%96%E5%A0%AF%E5%AF%84%E8%AA%9E%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E7%9C%8B%E9%81%A0%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%9E&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJORURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=3ffdb077\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210207%2Fs00002%2F1612636927791%2F%E3%80%90%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E3%80%91%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%B7%91%E5%9B%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%82%BA%E6%95%91%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85-%E6%B2%88%E7%A5%96%E5%A0%AF%E5%AF%84%E8%AA%9E%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E7%9C%8B%E9%81%A0%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%9E&h=a2c9e169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20210207/s00002/1612636927791/【周日人物】反修例衝突-跑回中大為救傷者-沈祖堯寄語年輕人看遠一點</a>"},{"pid":"3e0cc265424b6b57fe0bb7c6f7a10eca12e813e9","tid":2398303,"uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:36:24.000Z","msg":"沈祖堯呢啲真係有建設性夠實際嘅說話<br />\n起碼唔會鳩叫大家繼續努力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢都叫大家走，連登